Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.40,0:00:13.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我的房間
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.40,0:00:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我不會還沒睡醒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.87,0:00:21.07,Default,,0,0,0,,住手  再讓我睡會兒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.10,0:00:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,難得我夢到在大冒險中找到了最舒服的枕頭
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.52,0:00:27.57,Comment,,0,0,0,,get
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.10,0:00:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,那到底是什麼樣的大冒險
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.85,0:00:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,那不是夢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.77,0:00:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,那就是說…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.05,0:00:41.43,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}Everytime I want a deal
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.57,0:00:55.99,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}騒ぐ内なる声を聞け
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.57,0:00:55.99,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}聆聽你躁動的心聲
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.24,0:00:59.20,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}選ぶ道は決まってんだ stand up
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.24,0:00:59.20,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}你該選擇的路早已有定數 stand up
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.32,0:01:02.41,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}Feel my pain 現實和悲傷融為一體
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.37,0:01:02.41,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}Feel my pain 哀しみ混在したリアル
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.49,0:01:05.58,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}もう砕いた罪も続くと知れ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.49,0:01:05.58,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}盡快認清破碎的罪惡永遠都無法泯滅
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.83,0:01:08.12,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}飢えて spend the night with 混戦した
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.83,0:01:08.12,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}渴求著 spend the night with 陷入混戰
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.17,0:01:11.79,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}Part of the right to the right 流れ行く節操
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.17,0:01:11.79,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}Part of the right to the right 意志逐漸瓦解
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.04,0:01:14.26,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}叫ぶ love in depth and 断罪した
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.04,0:01:14.26,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}吶喊著 love in depth and 被判有罪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.38,0:01:15.76,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}Sort of the myth in life
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.84,0:01:18.43,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}神秘へ繋がった on the outside
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.84,0:01:18.43,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}和神秘緊密相連 on the outside
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.88,0:01:22.18,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}Broken I've never heard of such a thing
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.31,0:01:24.77,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}闇を支配した気でいたのさ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.31,0:01:24.77,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}一直自認為能完美駕馭黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.22,0:01:28.44,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}Vanishing I've never learned on such a thing
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.52,0:01:30.44,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}Well go straight down now
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.77,0:01:31.77,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}Deal
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.32,0:01:39.24,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}Everytime I got a chance
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.45,0:01:41.66,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}Said to me in the mirror
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.74,0:01:43.74,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}Won't you come over here?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.83,0:01:48.71,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}正しい光の影へ導かれていた
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.83,0:01:48.71,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}正義的光影指引著我向前
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.96,0:01:51.75,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}Everytime I lost my fame
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.08,0:01:54.34,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}Talk to you in the daylight
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.38,0:01:56.38,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}What are you waiting for?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.46,0:02:00.22,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}傷負う光の罪が消し去る
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.46,0:02:00.22,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}光芒的罪名抹除我所背負的傷痛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.26,0:02:01.76,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}夢へ be your own
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.26,0:02:01.76,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}邁向夢想 be your own
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.84,0:02:03.01,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}Restart
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.45,0:02:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,龍征!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.55,0:02:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,真晝  我以為你今天休息呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.30,0:02:11.25,Comment,,0,0,0,,櫻哉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.40,0:02:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,,龍征呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.07,0:02:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,櫻哉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.12,0:02:22.87,Default,,0,0,0,,右手  這樣就行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.90,0:02:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,龍征
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.80,0:02:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,真晝  你來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.47,0:02:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,你剛剛那副表情是想怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.42,0:02:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,因為真晝太嚴肅了所以我就想順勢逗逗你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.72,0:02:35.92,Comment,,0,0,0,,我錯了我錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.57,0:02:37.97,Default,,0,0,0,,龍征  你的脖子沒事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.62,0:02:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.15,0:02:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,說是交通事故  其實也就是稍微擦傷而已
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.17,0:02:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,交通事故
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.55,0:02:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,事故真嚇人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.60,0:02:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,,不對
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.82,0:02:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,昨天我們遇到的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.40,0:02:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,誒  魔術師是吸血鬼?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.95,0:02:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,你別嚇我嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.30,0:02:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,連真晝都變得跟櫻哉似的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.75,0:03:00.97,Default,,0,0,0,,話說你昨天沒和我們在一起吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.67,0:03:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,別說些奇怪的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.92,0:03:05.55,Default,,0,0,0,,快點準備文化祭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.92,0:03:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,有點奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.40,0:03:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,他們居然說我和吸血鬼昨天都不在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.77,0:03:12.47,Default,,0,0,0,,而結果卻莫名其妙地銜接上了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.97,0:03:15.02,Default,,0,0,0,,根本都沒人和我提起昨天那件事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.90,0:03:17.47,Default,,0,0,0,,完全不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.52,0:03:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我肚子餓了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.00,0:03:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,住手…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.75,0:03:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,閉嘴  你這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.17,0:03:23.65,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼時候進來的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.77,0:03:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我肚子餓了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.15,0:03:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,好想喝血啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.40,0:03:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,你給我喝一點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.82,0:03:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.95,0:03:30.77,Default,,0,0,0,,話說到底發生了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.85,0:03:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,昨天的事情就跟沒發生過似的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.05,0:03:33.05,Comment,,0,0,0,,你看那個人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.15,0:03:34.47,Default,,0,0,0,,那是玩偶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.52,0:03:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,好痛痛痛痛  你幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.85,0:03:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,你這種人要是椿的話分分鐘就被幹掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.67,0:03:42.97,Default,,0,0,0,,這傢伙口中的椿到底是什麼人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.42,0:03:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,小黑  你認識嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.20,0:03:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,襲擊了我這隻善良貓咪的傢伙的消息  我怎麼會知道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.10,0:03:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你到底是貓還是吸血鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.90,0:03:55.47,Default,,0,0,0,,這種情況下簡單地想想
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.82,0:03:57.97,Default,,0,0,0,,那個叫椿的就是我們的敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.40,0:03:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,如果不對他做點什麼的話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.77,0:04:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,肯定還會有其他吸血鬼來襲擊我們
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.40,0:04:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,誒  太陽雨?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.85,0:04:17.52,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.62,0:04:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我說你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.47,0:04:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,好像遇到了一些有趣的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.40,0:04:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,來說說你最近遇到的最有趣的事情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.75,0:04:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,少年撿到的小貓實際上是隻吸血鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.00,0:04:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,少年讓那隻貓殺死了一個令人火大的魔術師
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.80,0:04:42.97,Default,,0,0,0,,有種好麻煩的預感
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.55,0:04:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,,難道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.77,0:04:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,這傢伙也是吸血鬼?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.50,0:04:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,無聊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.87,0:05:02.47,Default,,0,0,0,,喂  你別躲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.80,0:05:04.35,Default,,0,0,0,,不是你的熟人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.50,0:05:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,不認識
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.75,0:05:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,這傢伙眼神好嚇人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.82,0:05:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,吶  我在找這個
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.37,0:05:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,感謝你撿到他
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.60,0:05:17.27,Default,,0,0,0,,你好慢  椿Q
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.32,0:05:19.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我肩膀都麻了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.47,0:05:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,椿Q?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.17,0:05:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,但得救了  謝謝你  椿Q
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.15,0:05:27.35,Default,,0,0,0,,椿Q  難道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.35,0:05:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,不會吧  突然就遇見…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.72,0:05:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,喂  等等  別想那麼多
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.97,0:05:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,還是快想想怎樣從這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.72,0:05:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,對  我就是椿
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.85,0:05:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.47,0:05:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,挑起這場爭端的就是我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.32,0:05:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.70,0:05:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,想要殺死好多的吸血鬼和人類的傢伙就是我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.20,0:05:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.85,0:05:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我現在很憂鬱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.72,0:05:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs32\pos(785,660)}Sleepy Ash
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.72,0:05:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我說 「懶惰」沉默之終結
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.20,0:05:59.47,Default,,0,0,0,,你來說點有趣的事情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.87,0:06:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你無話可說的話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.17,0:06:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,那就開戰吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.22,0:06:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼  你在說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.22,0:06:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,,你說是吧  哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.40,0:06:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.45,0:06:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你是小黑的弟弟?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.47,0:06:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,不不不  你認錯人了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.60,0:06:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我不認識你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.15,0:06:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,好過分  你好過分啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.22,0:06:23.02,Default,,0,0,0,,你也不認識我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.12,0:06:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs32\pos(445,660)}Servamp
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.12,0:06:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,結果吸血鬼僕人的兄弟們一個都不認識我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.87,0:06:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道一共有幾個吸血鬼僕人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.55,0:06:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,七個
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.12,0:06:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,對  七個
