Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.60,0:06:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,,「傲慢」不死冥童
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.32,0:06:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs32\pos(730,660)}Doubt Doubt
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.32,0:06:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,「嫉妒」疑惑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.02,0:06:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs32\pos(728,660)}The Mother
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.02,0:06:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,「憤怒」為人之母
